sub_title: Certified Teacher of English as Second Language
summary:
Welcome to my linkedin page, please feel free to contact me if you need help with English training for your employees or in-company English courses. You can find me on Superprof.nl or click on my picture below to access the page.

I have experience working with adults, my aim is to target your business and learning needs.
For teenagers, I help them prepare for oral English examinations and I also coach them in the four basic skills of the language - speaking,reading,writing and listening. I also help prepare students who wish to take Cambridge IELTS and TOEFL examinations.

After years of working as a Web Designer, I decided to retrain and become an English teacher.
